name: treatment of used lorry with refrigeration machine, 16 metric ton | used lorry with refrigeration machine, 16 metric ton | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/13967/documentation

This dataset represents the treatment of used lorry with refrigeration machine, 16 metric tones.

The activity starts when the used lorry enters the waste treatment facility. The data on energy needed during dismantling are unknown. 

The activity ends by different waste materials being ready for further treatment.
